## Chapter Numbering

Files with numeric prefixes get auto-numbered:
- `01-introduction.md` → "1. Introduction"
- `02-architecture.md` → "2. Architecture"
- `A1-glossary.md` → "A1. Glossary" (appendices)

## Build Commands

```bash
make dev              # Dev server
make dev-with-pdf     # Dev server with PDF
make build            # Full build (site + PDF)
make pdf-full         # PDF only
make charts           # Extract and render charts
```

